      | You can upload any of the following file formats: chm, csv, diff, doc, docx, dot, dxf, eps, gif, gml, ics, jpg, kml, odp, ods, odt, pdf, png, ppt, pptx, ps, rdf, rtf, sch, txt, wsdl, xls, xlsm, xlsx, xlt, xml, xsd, xslt, zip.
